			<p class="lead mb-5 text-primary">Clinical Psychologist/Clinical Social Worker</p>
			<p>Clannad Counselling & Consulting is excited to be accepting applications for a Clinical Psychologist and/or Clinical Social Worker to join our team in either a full-time or part-time capacity.</p>
			<p>The ideal candidate would have professional training and experience as a Registered Psychologist or Masters Level Social Worker (MSW), exceptional clinical skills, and come with a similar relationship-based approach when working with individuals, couples and families. Familiarity or training in Circle of Security would be considered an asset as we often utilize this modality in our day to day clinical approach. </p>
			<p>Clinical experience with complex trauma is a valued asset. Potential candidates will fit well with our team, share our vision, possess an openness to collaborative practice, and have a desire to be a part of an innovative practice with an interest in research.</p>
