					<p>As a growing private practice located in the beautiful Annapolis Valley, NS, our clinic is based on attachment principles that focus on healthy relationships across the life span. We specialize in trauma and attachment treatment and provide therapy to individuals, couples, families, children and groups. We have special expertise in working with Military, Veterans, RCMP and First Responders.</p>
					<p>Our team is currently comprised of two clinicians, a Clinical Social Worker and a Counselling Therapist, as well as a full-time Administrative Assistant. Our atmosphere is warm, inviting, relaxed and friendly. We value maintaining this in conjunction with quality service to the clients we support.</p>
